{"TopicId":162189,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"How do I scale planets?","CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T01:44:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T01:44:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt says it all in the title, how do you scale the planets to be really 1/10th real scale, and yet have the correct gravities?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame with stars.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd while we\u0027re at it, how do you set up a moon orbiting two planets?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-17T01:45:28Z\u0022 title=\u002206/17/2017 01:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Spaceception\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheRagingIrishman","CreatedById":165004,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T02:04:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126548-wip130-sigma-dimensions/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126548-wip130-sigma-dimensions/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. impossible\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T02:09:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223094370\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221497665073\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165004\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheRagingIrishman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, TheRagingIrishman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1.\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126548-wip130-sigma-dimensions/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/126548-wip130-sigma-dimensions/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. impossible\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I guessed that, wasn\u0027t very sure though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCrap, so they can\u0027t orbit both in a wide orbit, \u00A0\u003Ci\u003Eor\u003C/i\u003E\u00A0can\u0027t orbit in a figure 8 fashion or something like that?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-17T02:10:37Z\u0022 title=\u002206/17/2017 02:10  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Spaceception\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheRagingIrishman","CreatedById":165004,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T02:59:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope ksp only allows for keplerian\u00A0orbits. That means your options are circles, ovals, parabolas, or hyperbolas.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-06-17T02:59:59Z\u0022 title=\u002206/17/2017 02:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJune 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by TheRagingIrishman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Espelling\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceception","CreatedById":152800,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-06-17T03:03:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223094405\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162189\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221497668372\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165004\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheRagingIrishman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, TheRagingIrishman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNope ksp only allows for keplerian\u00A0orbits. That means your options are circles, ovals, parabolas, or hyperbolas.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n:\u0027(\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, I can meet in the middle, have a large Rocky moon orbit a giant, with the moon orbiting between them (I\u0027m a slightly elliptical orbit) and just carry on with the rest of my idea.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}